::Prowl::

Prowl nearly jumps as he sees Iron Raptor nearly bite his hand off, stopping 
at the last second. He was wondering if this was some mean trick to get him 
back for the truck comment. He had thought that they had gotten past that..

He slowly slides his hand back, trying to get it out of her mouth, Mangus' 
message going unnoticed.
